headline: Cadence and TSMC Advance AI and 3D-IC Chip Design with Certified Design Solutions for TSMC’s A16 and N2P Process Technologies
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., April 23, 2025--Cadence furthered its longstanding collaboration with TSMC to accelerate time to silicon for 3D-IC and advanced-node technologies.
